          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/36216983-the-perfect-nanny">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Jaidee (spa, cc ski, casino-only upd rd prog) by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/42294189-roger-brunyate">Roger Brunyate</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/17295672-jaidee-spa-cc-ski-casino-only-upd-rd-prog?shelf=five-stars-books">five-stars-books</a>
          </div>
